node.text: This week F&W Culinary Director at Large @justinchapple  takes a cue from regional barbecue sauces to create three bold dressings to transform summer salads into hearty main dishes. Full of flavor and inspiration, Texas Barbecue Sauce Vinaigrette, Sweet and Tangy Mustard Dressing and Alabama-style White Barbecue Dressing will punch up any salad green on the plate. Find out how to add some 'cue to your greens through the link in bio.

🍽️: @recipegoddess 📸: @sarahecrowder

node.text: These elegant Breakfast Egg Cups with Parsley Gremolata and Mushrooms bake up in a proscuitto-lined muffin pan, so it's easy to make breakfast or brunch for a few days. We particularly like the leftovers sandwiched between buttered toast slices. Tap the link in our bio to get baking! 🍳: Liz Mervosh 📸: @antonisachilleos

node.text:
The tender, smoky, and pleasantly juicy cactus paddles of this Charred Nopales with Jalapeños and Spring Onions recipe get tucked into fresh tortillas for a very satisfying vegetarian meal. Served with beans, rice, avocado, and lime wedges, it's a feast! Tap the link in our bio for the recipe. 
🍽️: @aangievargas 📸: @protazio

node.text:
From Wi-Fi–enabled refrigerators to ranges with digital touch panels and in-oven cameras, we've rounded up 7 connected kitchen appliances to upgrade your home. Enter the world of the smart kitchen where a new class of appliances won't just help you get organized—they'll help you cook and entertain better, too. Tap the link in our bio to bring your kitchen into the 21st century! 
📸: @subzeroandwolf

node.text: This week F&W Culinary Director at Large @justinchapple  takes a cue from regional barbecue sauces to create three bold dressings to transform summer salads into hearty main dishes. Full of flavor and inspiration, Texas Barbecue Sauce Vinaigrette, Sweet and Tangy Mustard Dressing and Alabama-style White Barbecue Dressing will punch up any salad green on the plate. Find out how to add some 'cue to your greens through the link in bio.

node.text: Chef Paola Velez's (@smallorchids) Baba au Rhum Punch Cake recipe from #PastrieswithPaola starts with a homemade brioche that’s infused with a rum soak, covered with a citrus glaze, and finally, topped with a fruity rum punch coulis. Tap the link in our bio for the recipe. 📸: @antonisachilleos
